{"tid":2194083,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"金希澈14年前車禍被判「肢體殘疾4級」　醫警告：再跳舞恐無法正常行走","createTime":"2020-09-08T09:48:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T00:15:44.000Z","uid":74065,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5302d15bd13d8ade01dcc698a334657b6240b6e9","tid":2194083,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:48:14.000Z","msg":"南韓團體Super Junior成員金希澈因2006年車禍時留下的後遺症，身體不堪負荷，近幾次的團體回歸都未參與。近日節目《聽到傳聞SHOW》中，再次提及當年的事故，並透露金希澈在車禍以後，得到了肢體殘疾4級判定。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5126/d5126859.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5126%2Fd5126859.jpg&h=1d7cfb7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲金希澈在2006年曾遭遇嚴重車禍。（圖／翻攝《聽到傳聞SHOW》）<br />\n<br />\n在7日播出的《聽到傳聞SHOW》中，一名娛樂記者提到金希澈曾在2006年8月10日凌晨，在參加完成員東海父親的喪禮，回到首爾的路上遭遇了嚴重車禍，造成大腿骨及腳踝骨折，事故當天馬上接受了緊急手術，入院整整一個月才出院，隨後在10月再度進行了第2次手術，將固定骨頭的7個鐵芯取出，復健與治療過程受了很多苦。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5126/d5126854.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5126%2Fd5126854.jpg&h=8679eead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲金希澈在車禍中大腿及腳踝嚴重骨折。（圖／翻攝《聽到傳聞SHOW》）<br />\n<br />\n接著另一名記者也表示，隊長利特也曾透露金希澈「當時如果沒有繫安全帶，很有可能會死掉」，由此可見車禍的嚴重程度超乎一般人所知，據悉，金希澈在出院後得到了肢體殘疾4級的判定，令現場的來賓都感到相當驚訝。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5126/d5126856.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5126%2Fd5126856.jpg&h=c45ce9d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲金希澈在出院後被判定為肢體殘疾4級。（圖／翻攝《聽到傳聞SHOW》）<br />\n<br />\n之後，金希澈一邊進行復健治療，一邊消化團體活動，然而在2015年時，卻遭醫師警告「如果繼續跑跳、跳舞很危險，以後很有可能完全沒辦法走路」，隨後在2017年11月以後，為了身體健康，在與公司與成員們商議後，停止了舞台表演活動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5126/d5126857.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5126%2Fd5126857.jpg&h=08f6e94e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲金希澈在2017年11月以後便再也沒有參與團體的舞台活動。（圖／翻攝《聽到傳聞SHOW》）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/09/08/174750_b7e1dbe598ea464e49ad204e23c6e3bd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F09%2F08%2F174750_b7e1dbe598ea464e49ad204e23c6e3bd.png&h=f9636d28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n契哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99662d3220022d5fdc4a36367819b0b9e429b167","tid":2194083,"uid":240447,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:50:21.000Z","msg":"屌momo屌到腳仔軟"},{"pid":"19160883c62f5af59935685d31d6221dcc353622","tid":2194083,"uid":82359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"99662d3220022d5fdc4a36367819b0b9e429b167","tid":2194083,"uid":240447,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:50:21.000Z","msg":"屌momo屌到腳仔軟"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:52:19.000Z","msg":"可能食開殘廢餐"},{"pid":"194d24fc42481b88c6af6271794e731bfbec9ed1","tid":2194083,"uid":222918,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:53:10.000Z","msg":"Momo點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a754e641f08ddc4cc29eb8b97515d80b2a68652b","tid":2194083,"uid":143093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:11:14.000Z","msg":"有2蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09f0a5cac592b522a3dd0546bf27372d8e893287","tid":2194083,"uid":54579,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"19160883c62f5af59935685d31d6221dcc353622","tid":2194083,"uid":82359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"99662d3220022d5fdc4a36367819b0b9e429b167","tid":2194083,"uid":240447,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:50:21.000Z","msg":"屌momo屌到腳仔軟"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T09:52:19.000Z","msg":"可能食開殘廢餐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T11:14:33.000Z","msg":"Momo 我今日好攰，你自己上黎啦"},{"pid":"dd3bc78e9194